.It Ev MODKDE4_SYSCONF_FILES
Some KDE ports install files under
.Pa ${SYSCONFDIR} .
We want to have them under
.Ev ${PREFIX}/share/examples
or such, and just be @sample'd under
.Pa ${SYSCONFDIR} .
So add
.Sq file/dir destination
